{"tid":1821720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港接內地通知武漢肺炎個案仍為41宗","createTime":"2020-01-12T13:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T13:30:55.000Z","uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a19bbc1f89d2103fa7d6cf6eeec131f9137ec17f","tid":1821720,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心表示，根據國家衞健委資料，截至昨日，武漢新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎個案仍為41宗，其中一人死亡，7人情況嚴重，6名病人已出院，其餘病情穩定。<br />\n<br />\n中心指出，內地當局已追蹤到763名密切接觸者，全部已接受醫學觀察，當中46人已完成觀察，目前並無發現相關病例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502397-20200112.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502397-20200112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=7040fafd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502397-20200112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3f846564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502397-20200112.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"98bb9c0b7e3d21876cfaf1e96e8f773c2997b22e","tid":1821720,"uid":345524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:29:16.000Z","msg":"支那：沒事儿，没事儿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41dc630151fdff5aa9fe90177d595ddfb9d41c0a","tid":1821720,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"香港多過武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}